He taught me that after I got home.

712
00:35:09,160 --> 00:35:10,640
Your father is a chef, too?

713
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:12,200
Yes.

714
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:16,080
Please send my gratitude to your father.

715
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,960
I didn't know you just broke up.

716
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:23,600
I kind of lost my temper.

717
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,040
I hope you don't mind.

718
00:35:27,240 --> 00:35:28,840
But I have to say something.

719
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:32,720
Even though we got through today,

720
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,080
I don't have a lot of skills

721
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:35,960
to save you every time.

722
